metadata.name: Unravel People's ENS3
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's ENS3, which represents an inactive state of pENS3. User can participate in a new 3-digit ENS acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's ENS3 as credit. upENS3 can be claimed into pENS3 when the subscription successfully acquires a new 3-digit ENS.
